**🌟 1. Detailed Discussion of Flexbox**
Flexbox (Flexible Box Layout) is a 1D layout system that arranges items in a row or column.

**✅ Use Cases:**
Navigation bars

Centering content

Reordering items easily

🔲 2. Detailed Discussion of CSS Grid
Grid is a 2D layout system that allows placing elements in both rows and columns.

✅ Use Cases:
Complex webpage layouts

Image galleries

Dashboards
🛠️ 3. Basic Use of Chrome DevTools
Chrome DevTools helps you inspect, debug, and optimize websites directly in your browser.

🔍 How to Open:
Right-click → Inspect

Or press Ctrl + Shift + I (Windows) / Cmd + Option + I (Mac)

